13
00:00:34,915 --> 00:00:36,249
This one is okay.

14
00:00:37,451 --> 00:00:41,121
Would you like to buy one by the way?

15
00:00:41,121 --> 00:00:43,390
It's boring to drink it alone.

16
00:00:47,894 --> 00:00:49,262
I think that's enough.

17
00:00:49,262 --> 00:00:50,731
I need something else.

18
00:00:51,631 --> 00:00:53,233
Chocolate.

19
00:00:53,233 --> 00:00:54,668
Chocolate?

20
00:01:00,307 --> 00:01:02,342
Excuse me.

21
00:01:05,779 --> 00:01:07,814
Little busters.

22
00:01:08,582 --> 00:01:10,984
So rude.

23
00:01:12,819 --> 00:01:14,388
RJ is much cuter than them.

24
00:01:14,388 --> 00:01:15,989
Right?

25
00:01:21,428 --> 00:01:22,629
What are you doing?

26
00:01:25,532 --> 00:01:26,967
