27
00:01:27,868 --> 00:01:30,604
How can you eat Bai Lang's chocolate?

28
00:01:30,604 --> 00:01:32,239
I don't know that.

29
00:01:32,239 --> 00:01:34,374
I found it in the cabinet.

30
00:01:34,374 --> 00:01:36,209
Did you ask his permission?

31
00:01:36,209 --> 00:01:39,212
He's your boss anyway.

32
00:01:39,212 --> 00:01:42,215
I didn't know it's his,

33
00:01:42,215 --> 00:01:45,185
and it's going to expire tomorrow.

34
00:01:45,185 --> 00:01:46,620
Look at the date.

35
00:01:48,288 --> 00:01:51,258
