you can't eat it without permission.

36
00:01:51,258 --> 00:01:53,260
I know.

37
00:01:53,260 --> 00:01:55,495
So I bought a few more boxes.

38
00:01:55,495 --> 00:01:57,697
I'm not that impolite,

39
00:01:57,697 --> 00:02:00,867
