40
00:02:06,540 --> 00:02:07,307
RJ.

41
00:02:12,712 --> 00:02:15,048
Stop spacing out. Come to pay.

42
00:02:17,083 --> 00:02:19,653
What's wrong?
You're not used to shopping

43
00:02:19,653 --> 00:02:21,388
with people other than RJ?

44
00:02:22,022 --> 00:02:23,757
Don't think you are in a relationship

45
00:02:23,757 --> 00:02:27,561
and the whole world
will follow along, okay?

46
00:02:27,561 --> 00:02:29,729
Just take care of yourself.

47
00:02:32,999 --> 00:02:34,601
Did you bring money?

48
00:02:34,601 --> 00:02:35,569
No.

49
00:02:35,569 --> 00:02:38,238
Sir, card or cash?

50
00:02:38,238 --> 00:02:39,940
Card.

51
00:02:41,475 --> 00:02:42,375
What are you doing?

52
00:02:44,544 --> 00:02:45,812
This card.

53
00:02:45,812 --> 00:02:47,380
Thank you.

54
00:02:47,380 --> 00:02:49,850
The national ID number is...

55
