This one?

74
00:03:58,218 --> 00:03:59,686
Stop.

75
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:07,727
What's the matter?

76
00:04:07,727 --> 00:04:09,563
Are you in a bad mood?

77
00:04:09,563 --> 00:04:11,731
Yeah.

78
00:04:11,731 --> 00:04:13,667
I changed my shift

79
00:04:13,667 --> 00:04:14,935
