200
00:11:50,250 --> 00:11:53,307
♪With you, there are no regrets♪

201
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,261
Boring.

202
00:11:57,397 --> 00:11:58,865
What are you doing?

203
00:11:58,865 --> 00:12:00,700
Nothing.

204
00:12:02,065 --> 00:12:05,196
♪I like simplicity♪

205
