209
00:12:18,151 --> 00:12:19,452
and spent three days and three nights.

210
00:12:19,452 --> 00:12:20,586
I didn't even sleep.

211
00:12:20,586 --> 00:12:22,822
Take a closer look, okay?

212
00:12:32,999 --> 00:12:38,471
