223
00:13:20,213 --> 00:13:21,581
Forget it.

224
00:13:21,581 --> 00:13:23,716
No.

225
00:13:23,716 --> 00:13:26,085
Maybe there's
something urgent in the clinic.

226
00:13:28,154 --> 00:13:29,622
Pick up.

227
00:13:31,224 --> 00:13:32,458
Hurry up.

228
00:13:39,499 --> 00:13:40,733
Who is that?

229
00:13:43,803 --> 00:13:44,971
Who is that, this criminal?

230
00:13:44,971 --> 00:13:47,440
Wait a minute. Let me get this.

231
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:48,941
Get my coat for me.

232
00:13:51,310 --> 00:13:52,512
Wait for me.

233
00:13:53,479 --> 00:13:54,580
Wait for me.

