00:14:04,857 --> 00:14:06,792
(Why do you go there
to answer the phone?)

235
00:14:06,792 --> 00:14:08,794
(In addition to "Sure Enough",)

236
00:14:08,794 --> 00:14:11,164
(is there "As Expected"?)

237
00:14:13,799 --> 00:14:16,736
(It's a good thing
I got him handcuffed.)

238
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:24,110
