247
00:15:00,546 --> 00:15:02,515
Okay. Be careful.

248
00:15:03,015 --> 00:15:05,218
Hold on for 20 minutes.

249
00:15:05,218 --> 00:15:06,018
I'll be right back.

250
00:15:06,018 --> 00:15:07,553
