442
00:25:24,736 --> 00:25:27,840
Yes, even better than what you make.

443
00:25:27,840 --> 00:25:29,508
Say it again.

444
00:25:29,508 --> 00:25:31,710
It's on par with...

445
00:25:31,710 --> 00:25:33,912
The best is what I make.

446
00:25:41,019 --> 00:25:43,488
