451
00:25:52,264 --> 00:25:53,465
Here.

452
00:25:54,299 --> 00:25:55,534
"Sure Enough".

453
00:25:55,534 --> 00:25:57,102
Come in together.

454
00:25:58,036 --> 00:25:59,738
Ye Qiran.

455
00:26:00,873 --> 00:26:03,442
