456
00:26:03,442 --> 00:26:05,177
This is my brother's bistro.

457
00:26:05,177 --> 00:26:06,612
Oh, yes.

458
00:26:06,612 --> 00:26:08,747
It's been a while.

459
00:26:08,747 --> 00:26:10,315
