503
00:27:57,189 --> 00:27:59,191
for myself and my family.

504
00:28:00,692 --> 00:28:04,329
I thought that was happiness then.

505
00:28:08,300 --> 00:28:11,069
I seem to understand you suddenly.

506
00:28:11,937 --> 00:28:14,506
