made you feel inferior,

507
00:28:14,506 --> 00:28:18,110
and my past made me feel guilty.

508
00:28:18,110 --> 00:28:19,144
Yes, Xun'an is so good

509
00:28:19,144 --> 00:28:22,881
that we don't know what to do.

510
00:28:24,783 --> 00:28:27,386
So, in the process of moving forward,

511
00:28:27,386 --> 00:28:29,821
