531
00:29:41,193 --> 00:29:41,760
No.

532
00:29:41,760 --> 00:29:42,861
No?

533
00:29:42,861 --> 00:29:44,663
I'm telling you, this lady

534
00:29:44,663 --> 00:29:47,199
used to be super cranky.

535
00:29:47,199 --> 00:29:47,966
